ttings Presents Error When you Select Auth or Embedding Sections","docs - note on pinning","Add documentation for password settings on Metabase Cloud","docs - clarify JWT Identity Provider URI instructions","Manual backport of preserving table whitespaces changes","Postgres queries fail with `java.lang.Class.isArray()` errors after upgrade to v0.56.3","A caret cursor is not visible in filter inputs","Content layout shift when checking an item in a collection","Pivot table export outputs blank values when pivoting on integer columns","Auto-update documentation for release-x.56.x","Better branch detection if relevant files are changed for CI","Fix flaky UpdatesNavItem test","Update Debian/systemd docs","Fix references to pre-56 Troubleshooting admin menu","Drill through no longer works for pivot tables in the latest version","Fix flaky test for metabase-browser custom element","Card filters seem to be avoiding the linkage to dashboard filters","Discard cached field values will... refresh the values?","Fix tabs alignment for horizontal tabs with grow (#61895)","docs: translations limitations","skip flaky loki row chart tests","There are more selected columns than there are total columns","refactor(sdk): Rename embedding-sdk directory to embedding-sdk-bundle","chore: upgrade vulnerable cipher-base package","chore: upgrade vulnerable sha.js package","[BOT-316] Metabase BE support for dynamic agent profiles","Respond with HTTP status 500 when Store API request fails during Cloud migration","fix(sdk): Add background-light to derived colors for the new embed","Content Translation doesn't translate pivot table columns","publicly-shared dashboards show blank pages when viewed in incognito (or by non-authenticated users)","[Metabot] Add `available_actions` to metabot context","Download button overlaps table header with embedding title is not enabled.","Cannot assign certain column types to fields in models","[QP] Don't apply `:coercion-strategy` to joined fields twice","feat(embed js flow): use widget for initial parameters","Fix invitation not being sent from /setup flow","Data picker skeleton is vertically shifted","[Search] Increase search reporting","Content translation copy uses wrong header name","[METABOT] Do not apply update-keys to ai-service request state","Cast to a Datetime doesn't play well with Joins on the Query Editor","Labels on inputs in the new-dashboard modal are incorrectly using font-weight: 800","dashboardId must be an int - error displayed for embedded maps with more than 1000 pins","bump arrow to 17 for parquet issue","Edit visualization on visualizer cards in dashboard view mode does not save the changes","Autosizing of tables on dashboards causes number to be clipped","Query Results are Temporarily Incorrect If Multiple Filter Changes are Made","Bad header alignment in filter editing sidebar","Upgrade fetch mock to v12","Changing field visibility to \\"Do not include\\" while filtering preview is open crashes the page","exlucde apache commons lang3","User who created Dashboard unable to change filters after Dashboard embedded with static embedding after embedding unpublished","[pivot] Optimize pivot construction for both backend and frontend","Statics Embedded Dashboard Export Icon Overlapped with Tab Navigation Arrow","It's possible to rename a dashboard to have more than 100 characters","Can't select filter values in dropdown via keyboard","Input not scrolled into view when tabbing into it","Ctrl/Cmd + Enter keyboard shortcut does not work to run question that times out","Field Selection Lost when Aggregates added to Question","Command palette layout shift on open","Linked tables info can be empty even when model links tables","Error when using coalesce expression in question with joins","Query error is shown when not enough permissions to run it","Accessibility issue with Filters in Dashboard","Can't open archived model used in question","Model is being expanded to data sources after edit/distribute","Errors